Tony McCoy finished third in his 17,630th race at Sandown Park on Saturday . 
  McCoy has been champion jump jockey for the past 20 years . 
  The 40-year-old has won more than 4,300 winners in his professional career . 
  He was presented with the Champion Jockey trophy by Ian Wright . 
  McCoy finished his final two rides in front of 18,000 race fans . 
 